              want‚Äînot what others expect. By connecting with your future self, you
              uncover your truest values, desires, and priorities.
            </li>
            <li class="mb-4">
              <span class="font-montserrat text-secondary">
                üéØ 3. Focuses Your Energy & Intentions
              </span>Reading your letter daily keeps your attention and
